membership:
EIA is a member of the Species Survival Network (SSN), UK LINK whales and marine groups, CAN-Europe, Ecosystems Climate Alliance, the Forest Legality Alliance, EEB Waste Working Group, Seas at Risk and a number of marine litter coalitions. &#xd;
&#xd;
There are too many informal NGO relationships to detail, but EIA works or has worked in close proximity with many environmental charities, but particularly Telapak in Indonesia and the Wildlife Protection Society of India
